3692	 * flags are an xor between:
3693	 * + PROPAGATE_NONE (no propagation of command at all)
3694	 * + PROPAGATE_AOF (propagate into the AOF file if is enabled)
3695	 * + PROPAGATE_REPL (propagate into the replication link)
